(20, 'Manager Account & Finance', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">1- Monitor the day-to-day financial operations within the company, such as payroll, invoicing, and other transactions</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">2- Oversee financial department employees, including financial assistants and accountants.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">3- Contract outside services for tax preparation, auditing, banking, investments, and other financial needs as necessary.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">4-&nbsp;Supervising group Finance &amp; Accounts department for efficient and effective functioning.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">5- Preparing and verifying all Management Information Reports (M I Rs) including monthly/annually separate and group consol ideated financial Statements a long with variance and ratio analysis.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">6-&nbsp;Supervising entire payable section including routine payments, advances, suppliers\" reconciliations etc.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">7- Supervising bank reconciliations (Cash &amp; Credit Card).</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">8-&nbsp;Looking after various Banking and financial matters and managing effective relationship and liaison with different financial institutions.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">9-&nbsp;Seek out methods for minimizing financial risk to the company.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 59); font-family: Lato, &quot;Noto Kufi Arabic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">10-&nbsp;Implementing and developing accounting software and different management reports.</span><br></p>', 'M.B.A , ACCA , ACMA', 1, '2019-03-25', 'BH', 'manama', '', 'Financial Services', 'Clover recruit', 1),
