bsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">At least 2 years hands-on experience in the web application domain.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Strong server-side experience with back-end portal technology, such as ASP.NET, C++, C#, HTML and PHP&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Strong knowledge in developing applications using one or more following database systems: Oracle 10g/11g, MySQL, MS SQL Server 2005/2008&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Experience in Microsoft SharePoint, Microsoft Dynamics and Microsoft .NET are essential&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">High levels of initiative and strong capability of multitasking&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Strong problem-solving and analytical skills.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Exceptional written and verbal communication skills, including the ability to present complex information in a succinct and easily acceptable manner, and the ability to work pro-actively with others to define and deliver integrated solutions.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Effectively articulate the vision and strategy of the system during reviews and/or team meetings&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Must be a self-motivated person with a drive for continuous learning and improvement.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Must be presentable and self-confident.</span><br></p>', 'Strong knowledge in developing applications using one or more following database systems: Oracle 10g/11g, MySQL, MS SQL Server 2005/2008 ', 1, '2019-03-25', 'AD', 'Manama', '', 'Information Technology', '01 Systems W.L.L', 1),
(31, 'Business Development Manager', '<ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Formulate sales management policies for Bahrain markets according to the business development stage and strategy orientation, including but not limited to: sales performance incentive, agent management, business distribution, etc. And promote implementation and tracking;</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Establish a local sales business data tracking and monitoring system, analyze and interprete sales business data in depth, monitor all links, find existing problems and assist in developing corresponding solutions;</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Understand the headquarters strategies and targets, identify desired external resources and use cases that can add value to the users and drive growth.</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">BA/BS degree in marketing, advertising, technology or media field.</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Native Arabic speaker and excellent verbal and written English communication skills. Communication in Chinese, would be preferred, but not necessary.</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Minimum 5 years of Business Development experience in major banks/finance institutions/E- Commerce/Telecom/Retail industry 1st tier companies.</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Excellent ability to analyze and solve problems. Great logical and data sensitivity;</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Based in Bahrain</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Job Types: Full-time, Part-time</p><p style=\"marg