e-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">System Security Administration and Documentation</b><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">experience, or an equivalent combination of education and experience</b></li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Candidate should hold current Security+ certification, CISSP, CISM, OSSP, or be able to achieve certification within 6 months of hire.</b></li></ul><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Familiarity with the new ICD 503, Risk Management Framework is a must</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Candidate must be willing to work a flexible job schedule to include off-shift work and occasional overtime.</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Analyzing system specifications and translating to software requirements.</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Well versed in NIST 800-53 standards.</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Sets the highest ethical standards for self and others</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Some travel may be required.</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">*About Wealthrs</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">*<i style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">We are an active member of the World Electronic Crimes Task Force and U.S. National Cyber Incident