ervices are used by the world’s leading law enforcement agencies, regulators, and businesses as they combat fraud, human trafficking, money laundering, and other illicit activity involving all kinds of cybercrime. We provide the most accurate rating of security risks for any organization worldwide, and we solve them. Our proprietary elite team help enterprises gain operational command of the security posture of their entire assets by offering a breadth and depth cyber, digital, and physical solutions not available from any other service provider.<br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">_</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Job Type: Full-time</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Salary: BD35,000.000 to BD50,000.000 /month</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Experience:</p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">ICD Coding: 5 years (Required)</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Cyber and Information Security: 5 years (Required)</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">System Design: 5 years (Required)</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">RMF: 5 years (Required)</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">NIST Standards: 5 years (Required)</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Education:</p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Master\"s (Required)</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">License:</p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">CISSP (Required)</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">CISM (Required)</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">OSSP (Required)</li><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">PMP (Required)</li></ul>', '............', 1, '2019-03-25', 'AD', 'Manama', '', 'Information Technology', 'Wealthrs', 1),
