(57, 'Account Manager (Sales)', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Main purpose</b></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\">Represent the company at all times in Bahrain and in the international marketplace, securing new business opportunities, maintain existing client relationships and increase revenue streams within those accounts in the form of up-selling by identifying new product requirements or benefits to the customer etc. Maintain a strong presence within the marketplace ensuring that all competition is equally matched and challenged with regards to products, services, and pricing being offered.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"></p><p><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Scope of the Job</b></p><div style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><li style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Continue to increase the company’s market share and growth by securing new