(58, 'Senior Account Manager | Kanoo IT ', '<div style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Senior Account Manager | Kanoo IT | Mameer, Bahrain</b>&nbsp;<b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">-</b>&nbsp;<b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">(</b><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">190091</b><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">)</b><div style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></div></div><div style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 13.333333015441895px;\"><b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">About You</b><div style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></div><div style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">We, at E.K.Kanoo, are looking for a&nbsp;<b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Senior Account Manager</b>&nbsp;who will be reporting to&nbsp;<b style=\"unicode-bidi: embed; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\">Sales Manager</b>. The ideal candidate for this role will have excellent English communication skills, both written and verbal. Arabic will be an advantage. The desired candidate should be mature, presentable, self-motivated, possess excellent interpersonal and customer handling skills in addition to being a team player. To be considered for this position, you would have completed a Bachelor’s Degree with an added advantage of professional sales certifications. A driving license would be required for this role.</div><div style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"><br style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></div></div><div style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Hel